  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A clinical study to determine the safety, efficacy and the way sitagliptin works in patients
      with Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus who have inadequate glycemic (blood sugar) control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
